* Provides a single extension point to process a response's content stream.
'"%s::stream()" expects parameter 1 to be an iterable of AsyncResponse objects, "%s" given.'
'Cannot stream AsyncResponse objects with many clients.'
// Ensure no exception is thrown on destruct for the wrapped response
'Failed writing %d bytes to the response buffer.'
'Instance of "%s" is already consumed and cannot be managed by "%s". A decorated client should not call any of the response\'s methods in its "request()" method.'
'A chunk passthru must yield an "isLast()" chunk before ending a stream.'
'A chunk passthru cannot swallow the last chunk.'
'A chunk passthru must return an "Iterator", "%s" returned.'
'A chunk passthru must yield instances of "%s", "%s" yielded.'
// Ensure the HTTP status code is always checked
'A chunk passthru must yield an "isFirst()" chunk before any content chunk.'
'Failed writing %d bytes to the response buffer.'
'A chunk passthru cannot yield after an "isLast()" chunk.'
'A chunk passthru cannot yield more than one "isFirst()" chunk.'
